## 🔹 9. Real QA Scenario (Philips type)

Call:

```
GET /features
```

Response:

```json
{
  "role": "FSE",
  "features": ["enumerator","connect"]
}
```

QA checks:

✔ role correct
✔ features correct
✔ no missing data
✔ no extra data
✔ correct type

Automation must validate JSON.

