## 🔹 10. Why JSON is important in healthcare testing

Because:

* Device data comes in JSON
* Backend sends JSON
* UI reads JSON
* Logs stored as JSON
* Config stored as JSON
* Role permissions in JSON

So JSON knowledge is mandatory.

